 08:00, and 16:00 UTC using the premium index methodology. The funding rate is capped at ±0.75% per cycle to prevent extreme funding costs. Long positions pay when funding is positive, while shorts pay when negative, with payments automatically debited from position margin. Phemex's low 0.01% maker fees make frequent position adjustments cost-effective for funding rate strategies."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
